texts.text:
Map, an item which provides an overview of the surrounding terrain
Explorer Map, a map that locates a monument, woodland mansion, or buried treasure, depending on the type
The Overworld, the main area (i.e. map) of the game
The World, the entire area (i.e. map) of the game, including all of its dimensions
Obfuscation map
Map (Minecraft Earth), the game's real-world map using the players GPS coordinates
